name: Cinnamon Rolls
description: Cinnamon rolls with a crispy exterior and a soft, fluffy interior, filled with a sweet cinnamon-sugar mixture and topped with a creamy glaze.

name: Rye Bread
description: A hearty loaf made with rye flour, offering a dense texture and a slightly tangy flavor, perfect for sandwiches or toasting.

name: Chocolate Chip Muffins
description: Soft and moist muffins packed with rich chocolate chips, perfect for breakfast or a sweet snack.

name: Whole Wheat Bread
description: Nutritious whole wheat bread made with whole grain flour, providing a hearty texture and a nutty flavor.

name: Baguette
description: A classic French bread with a crispy crust and a soft, airy interior, perfect for sandwiches or as a side with meals.

name: Croissants
description: Flaky and buttery croissants, made with layers of dough and butter, perfect for breakfast or a snack.

name: Sourdough Loaf
description: Artisan sourdough bread with a tangy flavor and chewy crust, made with natural fermentation for a unique taste.

name: Danish Pastries
description: Delicious Danish pastries filled with fruit, cream cheese, or almond paste, perfect for breakfast or dessert.
